00:34:44.385 --> 00:34:45.730 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: But it's also inclusion.

00:34:45.730 --> 00:34:46.530 align:middle line:90%
That's inclusion.

00:34:46.530 --> 00:34:50.010 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: Oh, it's
completely oneness there.

00:34:50.010 --> 00:34:53.090 align:middle line:84%
So this meditation is you
become aware of your fingertips.

00:34:53.090 --> 00:34:55.969 align:middle line:84%
That's the first thing, just
to be aware of your fingertips.

00:34:55.969 --> 00:34:59.040 align:middle line:90%
And then you set your intention.

00:34:59.040 --> 00:35:01.580 align:middle line:84%
Now, I'm going to give
you the phrase that I use.

00:35:01.580 --> 00:35:04.580 align:middle line:84%
And you can make your own, but
I've used it over and over.

00:35:04.580 --> 00:35:06.830 align:middle line:84%
Many people-- it seems
to be really helpful.

00:35:06.830 --> 00:35:09.830 align:middle line:84%
So you have a word
for higher power.

00:35:09.830 --> 00:35:12.260 align:middle line:84%
We're going to
use divine spirit.

00:35:12.260 --> 00:35:14.300 align:middle line:84%
Sometimes, if you
say God, some people

00:35:14.300 --> 00:35:15.950 align:middle line:90%
have buttons that get pushed.

00:35:15.950 --> 00:35:18.040 align:middle line:84%
But Divine Spirit,
most people can handle.

00:35:18.040 --> 00:35:20.680 align:middle line:84%
And another word that most
people can handle is angels.

00:35:20.680 --> 00:35:21.480 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:35:21.480 --> 00:35:23.313 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: Angels are the
messengers of Heaven,

00:35:23.313 --> 00:35:26.610 align:middle line:84%
the energy flows, the vortexes
that come in and whatever.

00:35:26.610 --> 00:35:27.800 align:middle line:90%
But they're poetic.

00:35:27.800 --> 00:35:30.510 align:middle line:84%
So we're going to
say Divine Spirit,

00:35:30.510 --> 00:35:32.102 align:middle line:90%
we open our hearts to you.

00:35:32.102 --> 00:35:33.060 align:middle line:90%
So that's an intention.

00:35:33.060 --> 00:35:34.800 align:middle line:84%
Divine spirit, we
open our hearts.

00:35:34.800 --> 00:35:37.170 align:middle line:84%
That means we're going
to feel your presence.

00:35:37.170 --> 00:35:38.760 align:middle line:84%
Because in this
meditation, you're

00:35:38.760 --> 00:35:41.610 align:middle line:84%
going to feel the energy in your
fingertips, then your palms,

00:35:41.610 --> 00:35:43.560 align:middle line:84%
and it may go in other
parts of your body.

00:35:43.560 --> 00:35:45.870 align:middle line:84%
But see, if you're
feeling, you're flowing.

00:35:45.870 --> 00:35:48.180 align:middle line:84%
And when you're
flowing, you're focused.

00:35:48.180 --> 00:35:52.620 align:middle line:84%
So you're doing the yang
energy is focus, concentration.

00:35:52.620 --> 00:35:54.165 align:middle line:90%
But you're effortlessly flowing.

00:35:54.165 --> 00:35:56.520 align:middle line:84%
So you're bringing the male
and the female together.

00:35:56.520 --> 00:36:00.990 align:middle line:84%
Now, in "Yoga Sutras," that's
called Darrena and Dion.

00:36:00.990 --> 00:36:02.670 align:middle line:84%
When you can do both
at the same time,

00:36:02.670 --> 00:36:05.187 align:middle line:84%
advanced meditators
think I went to somatic,

00:36:05.187 --> 00:36:07.020 align:middle line:84%
which is something that
everybody's thought,

00:36:07.020 --> 00:36:08.370 align:middle line:90%
one day I'll have somatic.

00:36:08.370 --> 00:36:10.245 align:middle line:84%
Well, you're going to
have somatic right now.

00:36:10.245 --> 00:36:11.580 align:middle line:90%
Anybody can do this so easily.

00:36:11.580 --> 00:36:13.930 align:middle line:84%
Because we have access to
our male and female side,

00:36:13.930 --> 00:36:15.840 align:middle line:90%
we can do both at the same time.

00:36:15.840 --> 00:36:17.610 align:middle line:84%
And beautifully,
when you do this,

00:36:17.610 --> 00:36:20.607 align:middle line:84%
it also helps you balance
your own energies in life.

00:36:20.607 --> 00:36:22.690 align:middle line:84%
Because women are often,
when they're overwhelmed,

00:36:22.690 --> 00:36:23.880 align:middle line:90%
they're on their male side.

00:36:23.880 --> 00:36:25.810 align:middle line:84%
When men are passive,
are irritable,

00:36:25.810 --> 00:36:27.810 align:middle line:84%
grumpy, they're too far
on their emotional side.

00:36:27.810 --> 00:36:29.560 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: So you're
giving your energy away.

00:36:29.560 --> 00:36:31.343 align:middle line:84%
This gives you and
restores your energy.

00:36:31.343 --> 00:36:32.760 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: This
restores the balance.

00:36:32.760 --> 00:36:33.150 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:36:33.150 --> 00:36:35.170 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: And so how to
restore the balance--

00:36:35.170 --> 00:36:37.240 align:middle line:84%
so there's a
phenomena in nature.

00:36:37.240 --> 00:36:38.190 align:middle line:90%
One is fingertips.

00:36:38.190 --> 00:36:39.990 align:middle line:84%
That's the turn-on
switch because, see,

00:36:39.990 --> 00:36:42.090 align:middle line:90%
think about how do I touch you.

00:36:42.090 --> 00:36:43.048 align:middle line:90%
Fingertips.

00:36:43.048 --> 00:36:44.340 align:middle line:90%
So if you want to touch, feel--

00:36:44.340 --> 00:36:44.820 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Mm-hmm, anything.

00:36:44.820 --> 00:36:46.350 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: --spirit--
it's fingertips

00:36:46.350 --> 00:36:48.540 align:middle line:90%
is the turn-on switch.

00:36:48.540 --> 00:36:50.857 align:middle line:84%
And eventually, you
learn to do your toes,

00:36:50.857 --> 00:36:52.440 align:middle line:84%
and then your whole
body can resonate.

00:36:52.440 --> 00:36:54.240 align:middle line:84%
But the fingertips is
the turn-on switch.

00:36:54.240 --> 00:36:56.400 align:middle line:90%
So I just go fingertips-- boom.

00:36:56.400 --> 00:36:57.940 align:middle line:90%
The energies are flowing.

00:36:57.940 --> 00:37:00.300 align:middle line:84%
So we know in acupuncture,
there are these energy

00:37:00.300 --> 00:37:01.445 align:middle line:90%
channels in the body.

00:37:01.445 --> 00:37:02.820 align:middle line:84%
And when people
are sick, there's

00:37:02.820 --> 00:37:04.830 align:middle line:84%
always a block in those
energies somewhere.

00:37:04.830 --> 00:37:07.290 align:middle line:84%
And what they do is
they put a needle in

00:37:07.290 --> 00:37:10.260 align:middle line:84%
to cause painful
sensation because when

00:37:10.260 --> 00:37:13.565 align:middle line:84%
you have painful sensation,
energy flows there.

00:37:13.565 --> 00:37:15.093 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: And breaks up the block.

00:37:15.093 --> 00:37:17.010 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: And energy flows
and breaks the block.

00:37:17.010 --> 00:37:20.460 align:middle line:84%
So in acupuncture, they press
a point where you feel pain.

00:37:20.460 --> 00:37:23.340 align:middle line:84%
When you feel pain,
energy is released.

00:37:23.340 --> 00:37:24.940 align:middle line:84%
That's the energy
being released.

00:37:24.940 --> 00:37:27.280 align:middle line:84%
So like yelling and
screaming-- people feel better,

00:37:27.280 --> 00:37:29.010 align:middle line:84%
but they don't end
up healing anything.

00:37:29.010 --> 00:37:31.020 align:middle line:84%
They just release
the blocked energy.

00:37:31.020 --> 00:37:33.300 align:middle line:84%
When you eat a lot of sugar,
you release the energy.

00:37:33.300 --> 00:37:34.675 align:middle line:84%
When you take
drugs, you release.

00:37:34.675 --> 00:37:37.380 align:middle line:84%
People feel uncomfortable--
they go and eat a desert,

00:37:37.380 --> 00:37:39.060 align:middle line:90%
or they go and they take drugs.

00:37:39.060 --> 00:37:42.332 align:middle line:84%
Or they do things to lose their
energy because it's blocked.

00:37:42.332 --> 00:37:43.290 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It's too stuck.

00:37:43.290 --> 00:37:45.450 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: That's what tension
is is energy gets blocked.

00:37:45.450 --> 00:37:46.450 align:middle line:90%
And what is that energy?

00:37:46.450 --> 00:37:49.360 align:middle line:84%
It's divine energy
that becomes blocked.

00:37:49.360 --> 00:37:52.120 align:middle line:84%
So that's, on the
surface, it's tension.

00:37:52.120 --> 00:37:54.690 align:middle line:84%
But if you go a little deeper,
it's negative emotions.

00:37:54.690 --> 00:37:58.620 align:middle line:84%
All negative emotions are
divine energy, love energy,

00:37:58.620 --> 00:38:02.700 align:middle line:84%
positive desire, soul
desire, good desire to serve,

00:38:02.700 --> 00:38:04.620 align:middle line:84%
to be of love, to
love and be loved.

00:38:04.620 --> 00:38:07.110 align:middle line:84%
That energy's flowing, and
it's something we do to stop.

00:38:07.110 --> 00:38:08.230 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: It gets stuck.

00:38:08.230 --> 00:38:08.910 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: It gets stuck.

00:38:08.910 --> 00:38:09.390 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Gotcha.

00:38:09.390 --> 00:38:11.970 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: So as soon as there's
a block, and energy's flowing,

00:38:11.970 --> 00:38:15.600 align:middle line:84%
now that tension builds, and
that's a negative emotion.

00:38:15.600 --> 00:38:16.890 align:middle line:90%
So part of this technique--

00:38:16.890 --> 00:38:18.240 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: I'm sorry, that
makes perfect sense.

00:38:18.240 --> 00:38:20.500 align:middle line:84%
If you're going in a direction
with a passion or something

00:38:20.500 --> 00:38:21.810 align:middle line:84%
that you really thought
was going to work out,

00:38:21.810 --> 00:38:24.000 align:middle line:84%
and it all of a sudden
gets stuck or jolted

00:38:24.000 --> 00:38:26.610 align:middle line:84%
or ripped away
from you, it does--

00:38:26.610 --> 00:38:27.960 align:middle line:90%
it sticks the energy.

00:38:27.960 --> 00:38:31.210 align:middle line:84%
It freezes it right where it
was in the motion of love.

00:38:31.210 --> 00:38:32.010 align:middle line:90%
Mm-hmm.

00:38:32.010 --> 00:38:33.885 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: So in the Daoist
philosophy in China,

00:38:33.885 --> 00:38:36.840 align:middle line:84%
they call that blocked energy,
stuck energy, stale energy.

00:38:36.840 --> 00:38:39.300 align:middle line:84%
In therapy, we have people
talk about their emotions,

00:38:39.300 --> 00:38:40.310 align:middle line:90%
and they feel better.

00:38:40.310 --> 00:38:41.110 align:middle line:90%
What is that?

00:38:41.110 --> 00:38:44.850 align:middle line:84%
It's because if you can express
emotion, and something else--

00:38:44.850 --> 00:38:47.560 align:middle line:84%
if somebody else can feel it
with you so you're not alone

00:38:47.560 --> 00:38:48.360 align:middle line:90%
in it--

00:38:48.360 --> 00:38:49.830 align:middle line:90%
a bigger healing happens.

00:38:49.830 --> 00:38:51.480 align:middle line:84%
Just being in touch
with your feelings

00:38:51.480 --> 00:38:53.340 align:middle line:90%
is good to let them go.

00:38:53.340 --> 00:38:55.050 align:middle line:84%
But if there's somebody
listening to you,

00:38:55.050 --> 00:38:57.745 align:middle line:84%
it's easier to let it go
because there's a permission.

00:38:57.745 --> 00:38:58.040 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Permission.

00:38:58.040 --> 00:38:58.740 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: There's an empathy.

00:38:58.740 --> 00:38:59.250 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Connection.

00:38:59.250 --> 00:39:00.450 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: There's a love
that says I understand.

00:39:00.450 --> 00:39:01.250 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:39:01.250 --> 00:39:03.930 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: So understanding
and empathy help release it.

00:39:03.930 --> 00:39:07.590 align:middle line:84%
So in this meditation, we're
going to use our fingertips.

00:39:07.590 --> 00:39:09.370 align:middle line:84%
We're going to
call in the spirit.

00:39:09.370 --> 00:39:11.025 align:middle line:84%
Now, the spirit is
always here, right?

00:39:11.025 --> 00:39:12.900 align:middle line:84%
But we're going to bring
our awareness to it.

00:39:12.900 --> 00:39:13.500 align:middle line:90%
That's all it is.

00:39:13.500 --> 00:39:15.280 align:middle line:84%
It's stating, out
loud, our intention.

00:39:15.280 --> 00:39:17.370 align:middle line:84%
So what phrase--
it's very simple.

00:39:17.370 --> 00:39:21.240 align:middle line:84%
It's Divine Spirit, my
heart is open to you.

00:39:21.240 --> 00:39:22.740 align:middle line:84%
If we're doing it
together, it would

00:39:22.740 --> 00:39:24.430 align:middle line:90%
be our hearts are open to you.

00:39:24.430 --> 00:39:28.076 align:middle line:84%
Come-- now when you say come,
you feel it right there.

00:39:28.076 --> 00:39:28.876 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes, I do.

00:39:28.876 --> 00:39:29.876 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: It's just there.

00:39:29.876 --> 00:39:32.370 align:middle line:84%
So it's just Divine Spirit,
our hearts are open to you.

00:39:32.370 --> 00:39:35.460 align:middle line:84%
It could also be, if you
want, I open my heart to you.

00:39:35.460 --> 00:39:36.362 align:middle line:90%
Come.

00:39:36.362 --> 00:39:37.820 align:middle line:84%
And then suddenly,
if you just have

00:39:37.820 --> 00:39:40.340 align:middle line:84%
the tension on your fingertips,
you get goose bumps.

00:39:40.340 --> 00:39:41.140 align:middle line:90%
It just suddenly--

00:39:41.140 --> 00:39:41.415 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's amazing.

00:39:41.415 --> 00:39:42.180 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: --starts to increase.

00:39:42.180 --> 00:39:42.510 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:39:42.510 --> 00:39:42.990 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: It's just as they come.

00:39:42.990 --> 00:39:44.610 align:middle line:90%
Now, that's three steps--

00:39:44.610 --> 00:39:45.750 align:middle line:90%
1, 2, 3.

00:39:45.750 --> 00:39:48.630 align:middle line:90%
Next step, I need your help.

00:39:48.630 --> 00:39:49.430 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:39:49.430 --> 00:39:52.200 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: So always, if you want
help, your guides are there.

00:39:52.200 --> 00:39:53.130 align:middle line:90%
The angels are there.

00:39:53.130 --> 00:39:54.350 align:middle line:90%
The universe is there.

00:39:54.350 --> 00:39:55.850 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And rarely
do we ask for it.

00:39:55.850 --> 00:39:57.360 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: And we
don't ask for help.

00:39:57.360 --> 00:40:00.202 align:middle line:84%
Because it's good to do--
you know, a child needs help.

00:40:00.202 --> 00:40:02.160 align:middle line:84%
At a certain point, you
want to do it yourself.

00:40:02.160 --> 00:40:04.350 align:middle line:84%
So the universe says,
OK, develop yourself,

00:40:04.350 --> 00:40:06.550 align:middle line:84%
but when you need
help, I'm here.

00:40:06.550 --> 00:40:10.580 align:middle line:84%
So it will come to help us
so that now we can co-create.

00:40:10.580 --> 00:40:12.550 align:middle line:84%
So that's the idea is
co-creating with nature.

00:40:12.550 --> 00:40:13.350 align:middle line:90%
I need your help.

00:40:13.350 --> 00:40:14.642 align:middle line:90%
I'm not going to do this alone.

00:40:14.642 --> 00:40:17.300 align:middle line:84%
I need your help because I'm
going beyond where I am now.

00:40:17.300 --> 00:40:18.100 align:middle line:90%
I'm in a rut.

00:40:18.100 --> 00:40:19.210 align:middle line:90%
I'm in my own place.

00:40:19.210 --> 00:40:21.142 align:middle line:84%
I want to go beyond,
so I need your help.

00:40:21.142 --> 00:40:22.600 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: But it's
not, do it for me.

00:40:22.600 --> 00:40:23.470 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: No, it's not do for me.

00:40:23.470 --> 00:40:23.800 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Gotcha.

00:40:23.800 --> 00:40:25.070 align:middle line:90%
There's a difference.

00:40:25.070 --> 00:40:26.430 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: Great Spirit, come.

00:40:26.430 --> 00:40:27.230 align:middle line:90%
My heart is open--

00:40:27.230 --> 00:40:27.430 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Is open.

00:40:27.430 --> 00:40:28.450 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: --to you.

00:40:28.450 --> 00:40:29.480 align:middle line:90%
Come.

00:40:29.480 --> 00:40:30.280 align:middle line:90%
I need your help.

00:40:30.280 --> 00:40:31.325 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I need your help.

00:40:31.325 --> 00:40:32.950 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: And then what
help do you need?

00:40:32.950 --> 00:40:35.630 align:middle line:84%
So today, the help we need, you
just have to set the intention.

00:40:35.630 --> 00:40:36.610 align:middle line:90%
The energy will do it.

00:40:36.610 --> 00:40:38.800 align:middle line:90%
It will flow just like your arm.

00:40:38.800 --> 00:40:41.560 align:middle line:84%
If I say to my arm,
up, it will do this.

00:40:41.560 --> 00:40:44.660 align:middle line:84%
If I cannot feel the
arm, it won't respond.

00:40:44.660 --> 00:40:46.720 align:middle line:84%
You have to feel the
energy of the universe,

00:40:46.720 --> 00:40:48.670 align:middle line:84%
the intelligent energy
of the universe,

00:40:48.670 --> 00:40:50.410 align:middle line:84%
and it will respond
to your intention.

00:40:50.410 --> 00:40:51.910 align:middle line:84%
And you have to
know how to do this.

00:40:51.910 --> 00:40:54.490 align:middle line:84%
And certain order to
it can help a lot.

00:40:54.490 --> 00:40:58.120 align:middle line:84%
Great Spirit, or Divine Spirit,
our hearts are open to you.

00:40:58.120 --> 00:40:59.390 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Our hearts are open.

00:40:59.390 --> 00:41:00.510 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: Come.

00:41:00.510 --> 00:41:01.310 align:middle line:90%
I need your help.

00:41:01.310 --> 00:41:02.357 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I need your help.

00:41:02.357 --> 00:41:04.190 align:middle line:10%
>>GRAY: And that's where
you get vulnerable.

00:41:04.190 --> 00:41:05.123 align:middle line:90%
I need your help.

00:41:05.123 --> 00:41:07.040 align:middle line:84%
And right now, the help
we're going to ask for

00:41:07.040 --> 00:41:09.548 align:middle line:84%
is to open the
channels for everybody,

00:41:09.548 --> 00:41:11.840 align:middle line:84%
so they'll be able to meditate
without me helping them.

00:41:11.840 --> 00:41:12.230 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Great.

00:41:12.230 --> 00:41:15.020 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: Is open the channels--
so the phrasing we're going

00:41:15.020 --> 00:41:16.650 align:middle line:90%
to use that is heal my body.

00:41:16.650 --> 00:41:17.450 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:41:17.450 --> 00:41:19.533 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: Healing-- healing
is opening the channels.

00:41:19.533 --> 00:41:20.540 align:middle line:90%
That's what it means.

00:41:20.540 --> 00:41:21.950 align:middle line:90%
Heal my body.

00:41:21.950 --> 00:41:24.110 align:middle line:84%
If you're emotionally
stuck or negativity,

00:41:24.110 --> 00:41:25.125 align:middle line:90%
you go, heal my heart.

00:41:25.125 --> 00:41:25.925 align:middle line:90%
Heal my heart.

00:41:25.925 --> 00:41:27.092 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Or if you have pain.

00:41:27.092 --> 00:41:29.960 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: If you have pain, it's
heal my body or heal my pain.

00:41:29.960 --> 00:41:31.940 align:middle line:84%
You could say just heal
my body is good enough,

00:41:31.940 --> 00:41:33.320 align:middle line:90%
or heal my heart.

00:41:33.320 --> 00:41:35.920 align:middle line:84%
And if you're really discouraged
in life, like beaten down,

00:41:35.920 --> 00:41:37.970 align:middle line:90%
this is my sweetest one.

00:41:37.970 --> 00:41:39.920 align:middle line:90%
Heal my spirit.

00:41:39.920 --> 00:41:43.760 align:middle line:84%
Because so many times,
we are so inspired,

00:41:43.760 --> 00:41:46.510 align:middle line:84%
and things don't happen the
way we want-- we just crash.

00:41:46.510 --> 00:41:50.310 align:middle line:84%
I remember one time, I
was a fraud of $3 million.

00:41:50.310 --> 00:41:51.930 align:middle line:84%
And I just felt--
it was tricked.

00:41:51.930 --> 00:41:52.730 align:middle line:90%
I was tricked.

00:41:52.730 --> 00:41:55.045 align:middle line:84%
It was all professionally
done fraud.

00:41:55.045 --> 00:41:57.170 align:middle line:84%
I just felt like, what
happened to my golden thumb?

00:41:57.170 --> 00:41:58.310 align:middle line:90%
Everything happens for me.

00:41:58.310 --> 00:41:59.910 align:middle line:90%
How could that be?

00:41:59.910 --> 00:42:01.250 align:middle line:90%
And my spirit crashed.

00:42:01.250 --> 00:42:03.860 align:middle line:84%
And I just had to meditate, to
come back to heal my spirit,

00:42:03.860 --> 00:42:05.120 align:middle line:90%
to believe again.

00:42:05.120 --> 00:42:07.670 align:middle line:84%
The universe is here to serve
and support us all the time.

00:42:07.670 --> 00:42:07.970 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:42:07.970 --> 00:42:08.770 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:42:08.770 --> 00:42:09.853 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: That is the truth.

00:42:09.853 --> 00:42:11.270 align:middle line:84%
And so we have to
keep coming back

00:42:11.270 --> 00:42:13.580 align:middle line:84%
to being able to understand
that and know that there

00:42:13.580 --> 00:42:15.075 align:middle line:90%
was a lesson I had to learn.

00:42:15.075 --> 00:42:16.700 align:middle line:84%
And it helped my
growth from the lesson

00:42:16.700 --> 00:42:19.000 align:middle line:84%
I learned from that, which
is not all people are

00:42:19.000 --> 00:42:20.000 align:middle line:90%
like me and trustworthy.

00:42:20.000 --> 00:42:21.910 align:middle line:90%
[CHUCKLES] You know?

00:42:21.910 --> 00:42:24.672 align:middle line:84%
You just figure, I would
never do that to somebody.

00:42:24.672 --> 00:42:25.880 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's a huge lesson.

00:42:25.880 --> 00:42:27.140 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: A lot of
spiritual people,

00:42:27.140 --> 00:42:28.280 align:middle line:84%
you have to get
that not everybody's

00:42:28.280 --> 00:42:29.600 align:middle line:90%
got the same ethics as you.

00:42:29.600 --> 00:42:31.480 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Yes, I've
learned that one too.

00:42:31.480 --> 00:42:31.940 align:middle line:90%
That's a tough one.

00:42:31.940 --> 00:42:32.600 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: Yeah, that's a big one.

00:42:32.600 --> 00:42:33.620 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes, it is.

00:42:33.620 --> 00:42:37.090 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: So we go through, Divine
Spirit-- now, for some people,

00:42:37.090 --> 00:42:38.100 align:middle line:90%
it can be, dear God.

00:42:38.100 --> 00:42:40.142 align:middle line:84%
Now, if throughout your
life, you're a Christian,

00:42:40.142 --> 00:42:41.690 align:middle line:84%
and you pray to
Jesus, then that's

00:42:41.690 --> 00:42:43.565 align:middle line:84%
better because you
already have a connection.

00:42:43.565 --> 00:42:46.970 align:middle line:84%
It's Jesus, my heart
is open to you.

00:42:46.970 --> 00:42:47.960 align:middle line:90%
Please come.

00:42:47.960 --> 00:42:49.370 align:middle line:90%
I need your help.

00:42:49.370 --> 00:42:50.570 align:middle line:90%
Or if you're healing.

00:42:50.570 --> 00:42:52.490 align:middle line:84%
If you need healing for
a family or whatever,

00:42:52.490 --> 00:42:55.370 align:middle line:84%
and you believe in Christianity,
you'd say, oh, Mother Mary,

00:42:55.370 --> 00:42:56.780 align:middle line:90%
my heart is open to you.

00:42:56.780 --> 00:42:57.890 align:middle line:90%
Please come.

00:42:57.890 --> 00:42:59.420 align:middle line:90%
I need your help.

00:42:59.420 --> 00:43:01.280 align:middle line:90%
Heal my child.

00:43:01.280 --> 00:43:02.240 align:middle line:90%
Bless this person.

00:43:02.240 --> 00:43:03.260 align:middle line:90%
Give her confidence.

00:43:03.260 --> 00:43:04.210 align:middle line:90%
Give her hope.

00:43:04.210 --> 00:43:06.260 align:middle line:84%
Or it could be, heal
my body to whoever

00:43:06.260 --> 00:43:09.110 align:middle line:84%
you have an affinity
towards, whatever deity,

00:43:09.110 --> 00:43:10.730 align:middle line:90%
spirit, whatever, or just--

00:43:10.730 --> 00:43:12.410 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: This so
beautifully simple.

00:43:12.410 --> 00:43:13.660 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: So beautifully simple.

00:43:13.660 --> 00:43:14.300 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:43:14.300 --> 00:43:15.620 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: Now, here's
the next step of it--

00:43:15.620 --> 00:43:16.420 align:middle line:90%
I need your help.

00:43:16.420 --> 00:43:18.770 align:middle line:84%
So you go, and you
hear a lot of people

00:43:18.770 --> 00:43:22.280 align:middle line:84%
who have had great,
miraculous transformations.

00:43:22.280 --> 00:43:24.210 align:middle line:84%
They always had a huge
amount of pain before.

00:43:24.210 --> 00:43:25.010 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: True.

00:43:25.010 --> 00:43:26.120 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: They have these stories.

00:43:26.120 --> 00:43:27.500 align:middle line:84%
They went through
all this stuff.

00:43:27.500 --> 00:43:29.670 align:middle line:84%
That means they're in
touch with their pain.

00:43:29.670 --> 00:43:33.065 align:middle line:84%
Their pain is the places
where light needs to go.

00:43:33.065 --> 00:43:34.940 align:middle line:84%
And light can't move
into you until you first

00:43:34.940 --> 00:43:37.220 align:middle line:90%
feel whatever pains you have.

00:43:37.220 --> 00:43:39.470 align:middle line:84%
And one of the challenges
for new-age folks

00:43:39.470 --> 00:43:42.280 align:middle line:84%
is we just want to live up
here and not feel our pain,

00:43:42.280 --> 00:43:44.030 align:middle line:84%
and then we wonder
where the passion went.

00:43:44.030 --> 00:43:46.760 align:middle line:84%
I wonder why I'm kind of
bored and stuck in my life.

00:43:46.760 --> 00:43:47.810 align:middle line:90%
We have to also--

00:43:47.810 --> 00:43:51.500 align:middle line:84%
part of the spiritual journey is
going into the darkness, which

00:43:51.500 --> 00:43:54.140 align:middle line:84%
is often called the dark
night of the soul, which

00:43:54.140 --> 00:43:56.610 align:middle line:84%
is, for me, when I was a big
meditator for all those years,

00:43:56.610 --> 00:43:58.193 align:middle line:84%
I was just rising
above, rising above.

00:43:58.193 --> 00:43:59.850 align:middle line:90%
But came out into the world--

00:43:59.850 --> 00:44:02.570 align:middle line:84%
I had to go through a dark
night of the soul, which

00:44:02.570 --> 00:44:03.440 align:middle line:90%
was I was homeless.

00:44:03.440 --> 00:44:04.430 align:middle line:90%
I lived on the beaches.

00:44:04.430 --> 00:44:06.410 align:middle line:90%
I was cold and scared.

00:44:06.410 --> 00:44:09.670 align:middle line:84%
And I thought, God, why
have you forsaken me?

00:44:09.670 --> 00:44:10.940 align:middle line:90%
Why hasn't money showed up?

00:44:10.940 --> 00:44:11.210 align:middle line:90%
[CHUCKLES]

00:44:11.210 --> 00:44:11.840 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: And you were here.

00:44:11.840 --> 00:44:13.400 align:middle line:84%
And you were helping
your brother.

00:44:13.400 --> 00:44:15.050 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: I came to California
to help my brother,

00:44:15.050 --> 00:44:17.633 align:middle line:84%
but I had no money, and I didn't
know where I was going to go.

00:44:17.633 --> 00:44:18.440 align:middle line:90%
And I had no job.

00:44:18.440 --> 00:44:20.900 align:middle line:84%
And I did have an old
car and a credit card

00:44:20.900 --> 00:44:23.930 align:middle line:90%
from my parents for gas.

00:44:23.930 --> 00:44:25.970 align:middle line:84%
So I would just drive
around from house

00:44:25.970 --> 00:44:27.587 align:middle line:90%
to house of women I'd meet.

00:44:27.587 --> 00:44:30.170 align:middle line:84%
And they'd make me dinner, and
sometimes I'd make love to them

00:44:30.170 --> 00:44:31.380 align:middle line:90%
and then move on.

00:44:31.380 --> 00:44:33.993 align:middle line:84%
I never wanted to
admit I had no money.

00:44:33.993 --> 00:44:35.660 align:middle line:84%
[CHUCKLES] But I would
be very friendly.

00:44:35.660 --> 00:44:36.790 align:middle line:90%
I'd read their palms.

00:44:36.790 --> 00:44:37.200 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: [LAUGHS]

00:44:37.200 --> 00:44:38.680 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: And then
my car broke down.

00:44:38.680 --> 00:44:39.810 align:middle line:90%
Then my car broke down.

00:44:39.810 --> 00:44:40.610 align:middle line:90%
Oh, my god.

00:44:40.610 --> 00:44:42.800 align:middle line:84%
I had to live on the
beach, and I was hungry.

00:44:42.800 --> 00:44:43.830 align:middle line:90%
A friend came to me.

00:44:43.830 --> 00:44:44.630 align:middle line:90%
He knew.

00:44:44.630 --> 00:44:47.570 align:middle line:84%
I didn't ask for help,
and he said here's $50.

00:44:47.570 --> 00:44:48.500 align:middle line:90%
You might need it.

00:44:48.500 --> 00:44:49.790 align:middle line:90%
He's my friend for life.

00:44:49.790 --> 00:44:51.110 align:middle line:90%
I'll do anything for this.

00:44:51.110 --> 00:44:53.600 align:middle line:84%
Because in those days,
$50 is like $500.

00:44:53.600 --> 00:44:55.478 align:middle line:84%
And you're hungry--
what a gift that is.

00:44:55.478 --> 00:44:57.770 align:middle line:84%
And again, when those lessons,
and when somebody really

00:44:57.770 --> 00:45:00.152 align:middle line:84%
needs help, you help
them, particularly,

00:45:00.152 --> 00:45:01.610 align:middle line:84%
if they have a
connection with you.

00:45:01.610 --> 00:45:02.750 align:middle line:90%
You can't help everybody.

00:45:02.750 --> 00:45:04.790 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: After a life of
celibacy for nine years,

00:45:04.790 --> 00:45:06.250 align:middle line:84%
that was probably
a gift for you.

00:45:06.250 --> 00:45:07.050 align:middle line:90%
Yes.

00:45:07.050 --> 00:45:07.850 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: Yeah.

00:45:07.850 --> 00:45:08.930 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yeah.

00:45:08.930 --> 00:45:10.550 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: And, again,
everything that

00:45:10.550 --> 00:45:12.530 align:middle line:84%
happens-- that was really
one of the darkest moments

00:45:12.530 --> 00:45:14.155 align:middle line:84%
for me is living on
the beach and being

00:45:14.155 --> 00:45:17.020 align:middle line:84%
scared because half the
people are dangerous,

00:45:17.020 --> 00:45:17.960 align:middle line:90%
are mentally insane.

00:45:17.960 --> 00:45:19.460 align:middle line:84%
They were thrown out of
the mental hospitals,

00:45:19.460 --> 00:45:20.877 align:middle line:84%
and they're just
wandering around.

00:45:20.877 --> 00:45:22.380 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Yes, this
is a huge problem.

00:45:22.380 --> 00:45:24.110 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: And so what I would
do is I'd be on the beach,

00:45:24.110 --> 00:45:24.980 align:middle line:90%
and they'd build a fire.

00:45:24.980 --> 00:45:25.910 align:middle line:84%
And they're sitting
around the fire,

00:45:25.910 --> 00:45:27.702 align:middle line:84%
and they're drinking
beer from their checks

00:45:27.702 --> 00:45:29.030 align:middle line:90%
they get from the government.

00:45:29.030 --> 00:45:29.830 align:middle line:90%
And I'm teaching.

00:45:29.830 --> 00:45:30.830 align:middle line:90%
You know, I'm a teacher.

00:45:30.830 --> 00:45:32.820 align:middle line:84%
So I'm teaching love God
and all these things.

00:45:32.820 --> 00:45:34.430 align:middle line:84%
And one of the guys
said, John, have a drink.

00:45:34.430 --> 00:45:34.970 align:middle line:90%
Drink some beer.

00:45:34.970 --> 00:45:35.770 align:middle line:90%
Have a good time.

00:45:35.770 --> 00:45:37.140 align:middle line:90%
And I said no, I don't drink.

00:45:37.140 --> 00:45:38.270 align:middle line:90%
And then, I didn't drink.

00:45:38.270 --> 00:45:39.710 align:middle line:90%
I drink now a little bit.

00:45:39.710 --> 00:45:41.780 align:middle line:90%
But I said no, I don't drink.

00:45:41.780 --> 00:45:43.340 align:middle line:84%
He said, no, no,
you should have fun

00:45:43.340 --> 00:45:45.860 align:middle line:84%
because we love
listening to you talk.

00:45:45.860 --> 00:45:48.440 align:middle line:84%
We have no idea what you're
talking about, but we love it.

00:45:48.440 --> 00:45:50.960 align:middle line:84%
And right in that moment, that
was such a key moment for me

00:45:50.960 --> 00:45:54.100 align:middle line:84%
because I realized, oh, this
isn't where I'm supposed to be.

00:45:54.100 --> 00:45:54.900 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Ah.

00:45:54.900 --> 00:45:56.810 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: Because I was making
my suffering kind of noble,

00:45:56.810 --> 00:45:58.320 align:middle line:84%
that I was helping
all these people.

00:45:58.320 --> 00:46:00.690 align:middle line:84%
But it was a very
important awareness for me

00:46:00.690 --> 00:46:03.090 align:middle line:84%
to realize you can't
help everybody.

00:46:03.090 --> 00:46:05.550 align:middle line:84%
You have to find what
you're here to do.

00:46:05.550 --> 00:46:07.460 align:middle line:84%
It took a while for
me to find that.

00:46:07.460 --> 00:46:08.790 align:middle line:90%
And that, you stick to that.

00:46:08.790 --> 00:46:10.740 align:middle line:84%
You can't solve all the
problems in the world.

00:46:10.740 --> 00:46:12.430 align:middle line:84%
You stick to what
you're here to do.

00:46:12.430 --> 00:46:14.300 align:middle line:84%
If I did everything, nobody
else would have anything to do.

00:46:14.300 --> 00:46:16.814 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: And you found that
through that deep, dark night

00:46:16.814 --> 00:46:17.066 align:middle line:90%
of the soul.

00:46:17.066 --> 00:46:18.845 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: Oh, again, I was in the
dark night of the soul there.

00:46:18.845 --> 00:46:19.000 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:46:19.000 --> 00:46:20.320 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: Oh, it was
such a scary thing.

00:46:20.320 --> 00:46:22.080 align:middle line:84%
>>LISA: Now, when did you
develop this meditation

00:46:22.080 --> 00:46:22.880 align:middle line:90%
technique?

00:46:22.880 --> 00:46:25.230 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: OK, so then, after
being married to Bonnie

00:46:25.230 --> 00:46:27.930 align:middle line:84%
and learning about "Mars,
Venus" and developing

00:46:27.930 --> 00:46:29.460 align:middle line:84%
our masculine-feminine
energies, I

00:46:29.460 --> 00:46:31.980 align:middle line:84%
realized that people are
having trouble with meditation

00:46:31.980 --> 00:46:34.560 align:middle line:84%
because they're more advanced
than the techniques they're

00:46:34.560 --> 00:46:35.580 align:middle line:90%
doing.

00:46:35.580 --> 00:46:37.650 align:middle line:84%
So these techniques
started coming to me

00:46:37.650 --> 00:46:39.900 align:middle line:84%
through the energies
that speak to me,

00:46:39.900 --> 00:46:42.570 align:middle line:84%
and learning how to
simplify it, and simplify it

00:46:42.570 --> 00:46:44.550 align:middle line:90%
so that anybody could do it.

00:46:44.550 --> 00:46:48.822 align:middle line:90%
And it's the concept.

00:46:48.822 --> 00:46:50.280 align:middle line:84%
See, we're very
logical people now.

00:46:50.280 --> 00:46:52.300 align:middle line:84%
People were not so
logical in the past.

00:46:52.300 --> 00:46:54.840 align:middle line:84%
So just use the concept,
the logic of, OK,

00:46:54.840 --> 00:46:56.920 align:middle line:90%
there's this great power.

00:46:56.920 --> 00:46:58.070 align:middle line:90%
I want to feel you.

00:46:58.070 --> 00:46:58.410 align:middle line:90%
Come.

00:46:58.410 --> 00:46:58.910 align:middle line:90%
My heart is open.

00:46:58.910 --> 00:46:59.090 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Heart is open.

00:46:59.090 --> 00:47:00.007 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: I welcome you.

00:47:00.007 --> 00:47:01.140 align:middle line:90%
My heart is open to you.

00:47:01.140 --> 00:47:01.940 align:middle line:90%
Come.

00:47:01.940 --> 00:47:02.970 align:middle line:90%
Come into my awareness.

00:47:02.970 --> 00:47:03.770 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: I need you.

00:47:03.770 --> 00:47:05.970 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: And then what I
learned from the masters

00:47:05.970 --> 00:47:06.940 align:middle line:90%
was fingertips.

00:47:06.940 --> 00:47:07.740 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: OK.

00:47:07.740 --> 00:47:10.032 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: They'd always just
be aware of your fingertips.

00:47:10.032 --> 00:47:11.520 align:middle line:90%
Just, instantly, it comes.

00:47:11.520 --> 00:47:13.570 align:middle line:84%
The next thing is
it would amp up.

00:47:13.570 --> 00:47:16.170 align:middle line:84%
I would do these healings on
people who are really sick,

00:47:16.170 --> 00:47:17.910 align:middle line:84%
and my heart would
feel bleed for them.

00:47:17.910 --> 00:47:19.860 align:middle line:90%
And I'd say, Mother Mary, come.

00:47:19.860 --> 00:47:21.000 align:middle line:90%
I need your help.

00:47:21.000 --> 00:47:24.180 align:middle line:84%
And bang, she'd come
so strong when I need.

00:47:24.180 --> 00:47:27.210 align:middle line:84%
So I realized needing is
such an important part of it.

00:47:27.210 --> 00:47:28.740 align:middle line:90%
Then directing the energy--

00:47:28.740 --> 00:47:31.120 align:middle line:84%
heal this person or
open the channels.

00:47:31.120 --> 00:47:31.920 align:middle line:90%
Heal me.

00:47:31.920 --> 00:47:33.860 align:middle line:84%
So heal my body is
a basic, simple one

00:47:33.860 --> 00:47:37.530 align:middle line:84%
to open the channels so you can
feel this energy in your body.

00:47:37.530 --> 00:47:38.940 align:middle line:90%
So I need your help.

00:47:38.940 --> 00:47:40.590 align:middle line:90%
Heal my body.

00:47:40.590 --> 00:47:41.880 align:middle line:90%
So the next thing--

00:47:41.880 --> 00:47:45.550 align:middle line:84%
this is why it's called
natural resonance meditation.

00:47:45.550 --> 00:47:47.310 align:middle line:90%
I'm taking the flowers.

00:47:47.310 --> 00:47:49.950 align:middle line:84%
And you'll see that if
you were a Catholic,

00:47:49.950 --> 00:47:52.020 align:middle line:84%
and you wanted a blessing
from Mother Mary, say,

00:47:52.020 --> 00:47:54.370 align:middle line:84%
you would go to the thing,
and you would offer flowers.

00:47:54.370 --> 00:47:55.170 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: Yes.

00:47:55.170 --> 00:47:56.250 align:middle line:84%
>>GRAY: You would
offer a candle.

00:47:56.250 --> 00:47:56.950 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: A light.

00:47:56.950 --> 00:47:57.750 align:middle line:90%
>>GRAY: A light.

00:47:57.750 --> 00:48:00.660 align:middle line:84%
You might offer some
gift-- whatever.

00:48:00.660 --> 00:48:01.760 align:middle line:90%
You give something.

00:48:01.760 --> 00:48:04.540 align:middle line:84%
Because, see, whenever
you give out of yourself,

00:48:04.540 --> 00:48:06.480 align:middle line:90%
you have space to receive.

00:48:06.480 --> 00:48:07.860 align:middle line:90%
So you're going to receive.

00:48:07.860 --> 00:48:09.240 align:middle line:90%
You have to give something.

00:48:09.240 --> 00:48:09.735 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: That's interesting.

